    <item>
      <title>一年过去了，特朗普的关税并没有帮助美国葡萄酒企业</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/dining/drinks/trump-tariffs-us-wine.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一年后，许多生产商表示关税对他们没有帮助，一些国家完全拒绝美国葡萄酒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/dining/drinks/trump-tariffs-us-wine.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 18:26:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪崩警告之后，内华达山脉发生悲剧</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/us/avalanche-lake-tahoe-deaths.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在现代加州历史上最致命的雪灾中，八名滑雪者死亡，另一名滑雪者被推定死亡。六人被发现还活着。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/us/avalanche-lake-tahoe-deaths.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 17:58:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙和平委员会：需要了解什么</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/01/19/world/middleeast/trump-board-of-peace-gaza.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统成立的新组织是为了监督加沙停火，但扩大了其职权范围。批评者称这可能会破坏联合国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/01/19/world/middleeast/trump-board-of-peace-gaza.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 17:01:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2025年货物贸易逆差创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/business/economy/imports-tariffs-trade-deficit.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国人口普查局周四公布的数据显示，由于服务贸易顺差扩大，美国与世界的总体贸易逆差有所缩小。货物贸易逆差创历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/business/economy/imports-tariffs-trade-deficit.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 16:40:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普正在考虑一项没有加拿大的北美贸易协定</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/business/economy/trump-canada-mexico-usmca-trade.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国官员威胁要对与墨西哥和加拿大的贸易协定进行重大修改，这可能会颠覆商业运作方式，并使加拿大陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/business/economy/trump-canada-mexico-usmca-trade.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 14:58:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一位瑞士幸存者讲述遭遇雪崩的感受</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/18/us/avalanche-survivor.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1993 年，海因茨·穆勒 (Heinz Mueller) 在瑞士阿尔卑斯山被埋在 30 英尺厚的积雪下，但他活着出来了。 “这是恐慌，”他说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/18/us/avalanche-survivor.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 14:49:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>糖碗学院称多名受害者被绑在其滑雪胜地学校</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/18/us/tahoe-avalanche-skiers-sugar-bowl-school.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这场致命长途跋涉中的许多人都与内华达山脉的一所专注于滑雪的私立学校糖碗学院有联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/18/us/tahoe-avalanche-skiers-sugar-bowl-school.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 14:16:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>和平计划与现实发生冲突，特朗普考虑在加沙建立军事基地</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/world/middleeast/gaza-rebuilding.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据该地区卫生官员称，自停火开始以来，以色列对加沙的袭击已造成约 600 人死亡。许多流离失所的巴勒斯坦人仍然住在帐篷里。还有大约6000万吨战争废墟需要清理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/world/middleeast/gaza-rebuilding.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 10:06:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在太浩湖雪崩恢复中，搜索者的安全是首要问题</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/us/lake-tahoe-avalanche-recovery-safety.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[天气和雪况将决定何时从山上取回在太浩湖附近雪崩中丧生的滑雪者的尸体。预计还会有更多降雪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/19/us/lake-tahoe-avalanche-recovery-safety.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Feb 2026 10:06:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
